{"id": 57795, "date": "2025-07-22T04:00:36", "date_gmt": "2025-07-22T11:00:36", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57795"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T11:05:23", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T18:05:23", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-22-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/22/kingdom-of-days-july-22-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 22"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>The Bruce Springsteen Band headlines two shows at D&#8217;Scene in South Amboy, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3163\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1971-0722/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1971-0722.jpg?fit=640%2C441&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"640,441\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-0722\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1971-0722.jpg?fit=300%2C207&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1971-0722.jpg?fit=640%2C441&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3163 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1971-0722.jpg?resize=640%2C441&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1971-0722.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1 640w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1971-0722.jpg?resize=300%2C207&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and his band headline two shows at Max&#8217;s Kansas City in New York, with The Wailers opening for them.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>It&#8217;s Night Two on the Born to Run Tour, and the band continues developing the show at the Geneva Theater in Geneva, New York, where &#8220;She&#8217;s the One&#8221; makes its tour debut. At soundcheck, Bruce and the band cover &#8220;Needles and Pins&#8221; and &#8220;You Really Got Me.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zaANhuBBSzc?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-57795-5\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/02-YOU-REALLY-GOT-ME.mp3?_=5\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/02-YOU-REALLY-GOT-ME.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/02-YOU-REALLY-GOT-ME.mp3</a></audio>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zBU71zy1szdg9oirFfoyzMi\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28427\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-07-22-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-22.jpg?fit=1026%2C1247&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1026,1247\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-07-22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-22.jpg?fit=247%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-22.jpg?fit=758%2C921&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28427 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-22.jpg?resize=758%2C921&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"921\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-22.jpg?w=1026&amp;ssl=1 1026w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-22.jpg?resize=247%2C300&amp;ssl=1 247w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-22.jpg?resize=843%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 843w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1975-07-22.jpg?resize=768%2C933&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19743\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-07-22/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1975-07-22.png?fit=1944%2C1751&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1944,1751\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-07-22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1975-07-22.png?fit=300%2C270&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1975-07-22.png?fit=758%2C682&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19743 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1975-07-22.png?resize=758%2C683&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1975-07-22.png?w=1944&amp;ssl=1 1944w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1975-07-22.png?resize=300%2C270&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1975-07-22.png?resize=1024%2C922&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1975-07-22.png?resize=768%2C692&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1975-07-22.png?resize=1536%2C1384&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1976</strong>: CBS Records holds their annual sales convention in Los Angeles, where Southside Johnny and the Asbury Jukes open. Bruce guest-stars with Southside on &#8220;The Fever&#8221; and &#8220;I Don&#8217;t Want to Go Home.&#8221;</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3171\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1976-0722/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1976-0722.jpg?fit=264%2C350&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"264,350\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1976-0722\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1976-0722.jpg?fit=226%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1976-0722.jpg?fit=264%2C350&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3171 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1976-0722.jpg?resize=264%2C350&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1976-0722.jpg?w=264&amp;ssl=1 264w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1976-0722.jpg?resize=226%2C300&amp;ssl=1 226w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 264px) 100vw, 264px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce&#8217;s Darkness Tour show in Birmingham, Alabama is postponed to September due to a throat infection.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"52625\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/the_anniston_star_1978_07_15_page_27/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Anniston_Star_1978_07_15_Page_27.jpg?fit=%2C&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"[]\" data-image-title=\"The_Anniston_Star_1978_07_15_Page_27\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Anniston_Star_1978_07_15_Page_27.jpg?fit=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Anniston_Star_1978_07_15_Page_27.jpg?fit=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-52625 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The_Anniston_Star_1978_07_15_Page_27.jpg?resize=758%2C885&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"885\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>Fresh off of his history-making East Berlin show, Bruce crosses the border to West Berlin and plays one show at Waldb\u00fchne.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLu8VBPtfGX1Ap7bmpnYqLbgqSwEfAqmhn\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1989:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Peter Hartung &amp; The Remakes on stage at McLoone&#8217;s Rum Runner in Sea Bright, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><strong>1995:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a surprise appearance at Tradewinds in Sea Bright with Joe Grushecky and the Houserockers for an\u00a0<em>American Babylon</em>-heavy set, with a few Springsteen originals added for good measure. Stevie and Max join for four songs as well.</p>\n<div id=\"v-0qtUKoWP-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/0qtUKoWP?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-ajyjMPPt-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/ajyjMPPt?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3181\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1995-0722/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1995-0722.jpg?fit=506%2C278&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"506,278\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1995-0722\" data-image-descripti