ploads/2020/07/1995-07-22b.png?w=1997&amp;ssl=1 1997w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1995-07-22b.png?resize=300%2C263&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1995-07-22b.png?resize=1024%2C898&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1995-07-22b.png?resize=768%2C673&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1995-07-22b.png?resize=1536%2C1347&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band rehearse for the upcoming Rising Tour at the Expo Theater in Fort Monmouth.</p>\n<p><strong>2011:\u00a0</strong>Bruce takes a stroll along the Jersey shore, stops and borrows a guitar, and plays &#8220;Born to Run.&#8221;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3193\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2011-0722/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/2011-0722.jpg?fit=450%2C451&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"450,451\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2011-0722\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/2011-0722.jpg?fit=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/2011-0722.jpg?fit=450%2C451&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3193 size-full\" src=\